All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Admin
Represents an administrator (admin) in the system.
AdminController
AdminController handles operations related to the admin such as blacklisting and whitelisting players, retrieving admin details by username, and providing a health check for the service.
AdminMapper
A utility class for mapping between `Admin` model and `UserDTO` objects.
AdminNotFoundException
Custom exception thrown when an admin is not found in the system.
AdminRepository
Repository interface for interacting with the Admin table in the database.
AdminService
Service interface for administrative actions in the system.
AdminServiceApplication
 
AdminServiceImpl
Implementation of the AdminService interface, providing administrative operations such as blacklisting and whitelisting players, and managing blacklist expiration.
AdminServiceImplTest
 
AuthenticationService
Service class that handles authentication-related actions, including extracting and validating JWT tokens from incoming HTTP requests.
Blacklist
Represents a record in the blacklist table for a player.
BlacklistDTO
Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing the blacklisting details of a player.
BlacklistEmailDTO
Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing an email related to blacklisting a player.
BlacklistRepository
Repository interface for interacting with the Blacklist table in the database.
DataInitializer
This class is responsible for initializing default admin accounts in the database.
EmailServiceClient
Client service for interacting with the Email Service API.
GlobalExceptionHandler
GlobalExceptionHandler is responsible for handling exceptions across the application.
InvalidBlacklistOperationException
Custom exception thrown when an invalid operation is attempted on the blacklist.
JwtRequestFilter
JwtRequestFilter is a custom filter that intercepts HTTP requests to validate JWT tokens.
JwtUtil
Utility class for handling JWT token creation, validation, and extraction of claims.
PlayerDTO
Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing a player in the chess system.
PlayerServiceClient
Client service for interacting with the Player Service API.
SecurityConfig
Security configuration class for setting up authentication and authorization for the admin-related APIs.
UnauthorizedActionException
Custom exception thrown when a user attempts an unauthorized action.
UserDTO
Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing a user, containing information such as user ID, username, password, email, and role.
WhitelistDTO
Data Transfer Object (DTO) for handling the details of a player being whitelisted.
WhitelistEmailDTO
Data Transfer Object (DTO) used for holding email-related information about the whitelisting process.
